<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>CORE ERP Multi-Tenant – Technical Overview</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <meta name="description" content="CORE ERP è una piattaforma ERP multi-tenant con architettura SaaS, edge security Cloudflare, API pubblica, automazioni e social monitoring." />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/modern-css-reset/dist/reset.min.css" />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background: #050816;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .page {
      max-width: 960px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.4rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: #fff;
    }
    h2 {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      color: #fff;
    }
    p {
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #d1d5db;
    }
    .badge-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem;
    }
    .badge {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      padding: 0.35rem 0.7rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid #4b5563;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8);
      color: #e5e7eb;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }
    .card {
      border-radius: 0.9rem;
      border: 1px solid #1f2937;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #111827, #020617);
      padding: 1.2rem 1.3rem;
    }
    .card h3 {
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .card ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding-left: 0;
    }
    .card li {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin: 0.25rem 0;
    }
    .card li::before {
      content: "•";
      color: #22c55e;
      margin-right: 0.4rem;
    }
    .cta-row {
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .btn {
      padding: 0.7rem 1.4rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #22c55e, #16a34a);
      color: #020617;
    }
    .btn-ghost {
      border: 1px solid #4b5563;
      color: #e5e7eb;
    }
    .small {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #6b7280;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="page">
    <h1>CORE ERP Multi-Tenant</h1>
    <p>
      Piattaforma ERP multi-tenant con architettura SaaS, edge security Cloudflare, API pubblica,
      automazioni contabili e logistiche, audit forense e modulo di Social Monitoring per analisi
      di interazioni e performance dei canali social.
    </p>

    <div class="badge-row">
      <span class="badge">Multi-Tenant SaaS</span>
      <span class="badge">Node / Express / PostgreSQL</span>
      <span class="badge">React 18 / Vite</span>
      <span class="badge">Cloudflare WAF</span>
      <span class="badge">Public API Engine</span>
      <span class="badge">Audit Logging</span>
      <span class="badge">Social Monitoring</span>
    </div>

    <section class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Core Engine & Auth</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Login centralizzato con multi-domain handshake.</li>
          <li>JWT interceptor con session persistence.</li>
          <li>RBAC: Superadmin, Admin, User.</li>
          <li>Ghost Impersonation per accesso controllato ai tenant.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Edge Security</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Cloudflare WAF, Anti-DDoS, Bot Management.</li>
          <li>Universal SSL/TLS su ogni tenant.</li>
          <li>Subdomain orchestration su *.bigbastik.de.</li>
          <li>IP backend mascherato.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Backend & Automation</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Controllers modulari (auth, invoices, warehouse, accounting).</li>
          <li>Isolamento dati via tenant_id (UUID).</li>
          <li>Accounting, Credit Recovery, Stock Guard.</li>
          <li>Audit logging forense.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Public API Engine</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>API Keys per tenant (Client ID + Secret Key).</li>
          <li>Storage hash HMAC/SHA256.</li>
          <li>Rate limiting per tenant.</li>
          <li>Swagger/OpenAPI su /api/v1/docs.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Frontend & Dashboard</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>React 18 + Vite + Tailwind CSS.</li>
          <li>ThemeContext per brand identity per-tenant.</li>
          <li>KPI globali per sottodominio.</li>
          <li>Layout responsive mobile-first.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Social Monitoring & Engagement</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Raccolta centralizzata di metriche social per tenant.</li>
          <li>Interazioni: like, commenti, condivisioni, click.</li>
          <li>Performance per canale (es. Facebook, Instagram, LinkedIn, X).</li>
          <li>Dashboard di correlazione tra campagne social e fatturato.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="cta-row">
      <a href="https://gestionale.bigbastik.de" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank">Apri la piattaforma</a>
      <a href="./docs/index.html" class="btn btn-ghost">Documentazione API</a>
    </div>

    <p class="small">Questo repository è una vetrina tecnica. Il codice sorgente non è pubblico.</p>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
